title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Robinson R44 Raven II helicopter  - version 1.1 beta
description:
In this video we are going to look at the latest beta release of the Robinson R44 Raven II helicopter. The developers worked hard to add several improvements and fixes to the helicopter just before the end of the year so join me to have a look at them.

If you also want to give the Robinson R44 Raven II helicopter a try download it the helicopter and the prereqs via the links below:

Helicopter:
https://flightsim.to/file/20566/robinson-r44-raven-ii-helicopter-project

AirlandFS:
https://nl.flightsim.to/file/21417/airlandfs

GMS750:
https://pms50.com/msfs/
